val sc = spark.sparkContext
spark.conf.set("spark.storage.synapse.linkedServiceName", "accvault1")
spark.conf.set("fs.azure.account.oauth.provider.type", "com.microsoft.azure.synapse.tokenlibrary.LinkedServiceBasedTokenProvider")

val df = spark.read.csv("abfss://tpchdata@accbbstore.dfs.core.windows.net/CUSTOMER/*.parquet")

display(df.limit(10))

%%sql
CREATE TEMPORARY VIEW customer
USING org.apache.spark.sql.parquet
OPTIONS (
  path "wasbs://tpchdata@accbbstore.blob.core.windows.net/CUSTOMER/*.parquet"

%%sql
CREATE TEMPORARY VIEW lineitem
USING org.apache.spark.sql.parquet
OPTIONS (
  path "wasbs://tpchdata@accbbstore.blob.core.windows.net/LINEITEM/*.parquet"

%%sql
CREATE TEMPORARY VIEW nation
USING org.apache.spark.sql.parquet
OPTIONS (
  path "wasbs://tpchdata@accbbstore.blob.core.windows.net/NATION/*.parquet"

%%sql
CREATE TEMPORARY VIEW orders
USING org.apache.spark.sql.parquet
OPTIONS (
  path "wasbs://tpchdata@accbbstore.blob.core.windows.net/ORDERS/*.parquet"

%%sql
CREATE TEMPORARY VIEW part
USING org.apache.spark.sql.parquet
OPTIONS (
  path "wasbs://tpchdata@accbbstore.blob.core.windows.net/PART/*.parquet"

%%sql
CREATE TEMPORARY VIEW partsupp
USING org.apache.spark.sql.parquet
OPTIONS (
  path "wasbs://tpchdata@accbbstore.blob.core.windows.net/PARTSUPP/*.parquet"

%%sql
CREATE TEMPORARY VIEW region
USING org.apache.spark.sql.parquet
OPTIONS (
  path "wasbs://tpchdata@accbbstore.blob.core.windows.net/REGION/*.parquet"

%%sql
CREATE TEMPORARY VIEW supplier
USING org.apache.spark.sql.parquet
OPTIONS (
  path "wasbs://tpchdata@accbbstore.blob.core.windows.net/SUPPLIER/*.parquet"

%%sql

select
       l_returnflag,
       l_linestatus,
       sum(l_quantity) as sum_qty,
       sum(l_extendedprice) as sum_base_price,
       sum(l_extendedprice * (1-l_discount)) as sum_disc_price,
       sum(l_extendedprice * (1-l_discount) * (1+l_tax)) as sum_charge,
       avg(l_quantity) as avg_qty,
       avg(l_extendedprice) as avg_price,
       avg(l_discount) as avg_disc,
       count(*) as count_order
 from
       lineitem
 where
       l_shipdate <= date_add(to_date('1998-12-01'), -90)
 group by
       l_returnflag,
       l_linestatus
 order by
       l_returnflag,
       l_linestatus

%%sql
Select 
       a.l_returnflag,
       a.l_linestatus,
       sum(a.l_quantity) as sum_qty,
       sum(a.l_extendedprice) as sum_base_price,
       sum(a.l_extendedprice * (1-a.l_discount)) as sum_disc_price,
       sum(a.l_extendedprice * (1-a.l_discount) * (1+a.l_tax)) as sum_charge,
       avg(a.l_quantity) as avg_qty,
       avg(a.l_extendedprice) as avg_price,
       avg(a.l_discount) as avg_disc,
       count(*) as count_order
from 
lineitem a join orders b on a.L_ORDERKEY = b.O_ORDERKEY 
join customer c on b.O_CUSTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
join partsupp d on a.L_SUPPKEY = d.PS_SUPPKEY
join part e on d.PS_PARTKEY = e.P_PARTKEY
join supplier f on d.PS_SUPPKEY = f.S_SUPPKEY
join nation g on f.S_NATIONKEY = g.N_NATIONKEY
join region h on g.N_REGIONKEY = h.R_REGIONKEY
 where
       a.l_shipdate <= date_add(to_date('1998-12-01'), -90)
 group by
       a.l_returnflag,
       a.l_linestatus
 order by
       a.l_returnflag,
       a.l_linestatus
